      • getChildFile

        public FileModel getChildFile(ArchiveModel archiveModel,
                              String filePath)
        Finds the file at the provided path within the archive. Eg, getChildFile(ArchiveModel, "/META-INF/MANIFEST.MF") will return a FileModel if a file named /META-INF/MANIFEST.MF exists within the archive
        Returns:
        Returns the located FileModel or null if no file with this path could be located
